    },
    {
      "text": "Bassin's Black Bass with Hank Parker, known in Japan as Super Black Bass 2 (スーパーブラックバス２) is a 1994 tournament-based fishing video game developed by Starfish (ja) and published by Hot B for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. It is part of the Black Bass series.  The player attempts to rise up from an amateur tournament to the bass fishing championship in both versions. In the North American version, the player must compete and win against Hank Parker for the championship.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Bassin's Black Bass with Hank Parker, in Giappone Super Black Bass 2 (スーパーブラックバス２?), è un videogioco di pesca sportiva sviluppato dalla Starfish e pubblicato dalla HOT・B per Super Nintendo Entertainment System.\nPer vincere bisogna essere i primi nel torneo di pesca. Nella versione americana, il giocatore compete contro Hank Parker nella finale.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Bassin's Black Bass with Hank Parker』は、日本で『スーパーブラックバス2』として知られる、1994年にStarfish（ja）が開発し、Hot Bからスーパーファミコン向けに発売されたトーナメント形式の釣りビデオゲームです。本作はブラックバスシリーズの一作にあたります。プレイヤーは、アマチュアの大会からバス釣りチャンピオンシップを目指して戦います。北米版では、チャンピオンシップをかけてハンク・パーカーと対戦し、勝利を収めることが求められます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
